sequenceDiagram
    participant B as Broker
    participant C as Consumer
    participant DB as 业务数据库

    B->>C: Deliver(event_id=E1003)
    C->>DB: BEGIN
    C->>DB: INSERT Inbox(E1003) + 更新订单
    C->>DB: COMMIT
    DB-->>C: 提交成功
    C--xB: ACK丢失或Consumer立即崩溃
    B->>C: 再次投递E1003
    C->>DB: INSERT Inbox(E1003)
    DB-->>C: 唯一约束冲突，识别为重复
    C-->>B: ACK成功
